Package: wUMAP
Title: Variance-Weighted PCA UMAP for Seurat Objects
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides RunWeightedUMAP() and RunWeightedNeighbors() for use
    with Seurat objects. Each principal component axis is scaled by a weight
    derived from its variance contribution before manifold learning, so that
    biologically informative PCs dominate cell distances. RunWeightedNeighbors()
    builds KNN/SNN graphs in the same weighted space, ensuring clustering and
    UMAP share a consistent embedding.
